Crashing through the lies and disinformation of the Mainstream Media, The Alex Jones Show is a nationally syndicated news/talk show based out of Austin, TX. The show is syndicated by the Genesis Communication Network on over 60 AM and FM radio stations across the United States, as well as having a large internet based audience. Alex Jones also has a late afternoon Sunday radio show aired on Emmis Communications\&#039; KLBJ 590 AM in Austin. The show is nationally syndicated in association with Genesis Communications Network.

The Bumper Music used on The Alex Jones Show is probably the most comprehensive soundtrack available to waging war with the New World Order. Because of this, we have created The Alex Jones Show Bumper Music Collection (Volume 1). 

Enjoy and please remember to SEED!

**This collection is fan based and not associated with Alex Jones**
